{"id": "5a4b15de-f129-47c1-967b-176492f1e2be", "knowledge_id": "һԪ���η���", "difficulty_target": 3, "question_type": "multiple_choice", "content_mode": "text", "image_placement": "", "stem": "已知关于$x$的一元二次方程$x^2-5x+6=0$，则该方程的两个根是(    )", "options": {"A": "$x=2$或$x=3$", "B": "$x=1$或$x=6$", "C": "$x=-2$或$x=-3$", "D": "$x=2$或$x=-3$"}, "answer": "A", "analysis": "将方程$x^2-5x+6=0$因式分解：\n$x^2-5x+6=(x-2)(x-3)$。\n\n所以原方程可化为\n$(x-2)(x-3)=0$。\n\n根据乘积等于0的性质，可得\n$x-2=0$或$x-3=0$，\n解得$x=2$或$x=3$。\n\n因此该一元二次方程的两个根是$x=2$和$x=3$，故选A。", "meta": {"source": "baseline_direct"}}
